Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.79,0:02:50.17,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}聽從內心之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.47,0:02:53.62,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}不再害怕孤獨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.74,0:02:56.01,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}看吧　勇氣能引導你貫穿而過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.09,0:02:57.10,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}paradigm shift
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:03:01.25,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}就算失去了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:04.87,EDC,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\an2}也要向沒有道路的地方前行
